  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read the canonical wrapper produced by Wave 1 task 022 + integrated by task 050: `src/client/shared/Spaarke.UI.Components/src/components/EmailComposer/wrappers/SendEmailDialog.tsx`. Locate the existing `ISendEmailDialogProps` definition.</step>
